 127:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_can.h ****  * @brief Controller Area Network Controller (CAN) driver for the XMC microcontroller family.
 128:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_can.h ****  *
 129:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_can.h ****  * CAN driver provides transfer of CAN frames in accordance with CAN specificetion V2.0 B (active).
 130:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_can.h ****  * can receive and transmit standard frames with 11-bit identifiers as well as extended frames with
 131:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_can.h ****  * All CAN nodes share a common set of message objects. Each message object can be individually all
 132:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_can.h ****  * CAN nodes.
 133:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_can.h ****  * Besides serving as a storage container for incoming and outgoing frames, message objects can be 
 134:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_can.h ****  * gateways between
 135:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_can.h ****  * the CAN nodes or to setup a FIFO buffer. The CAN module provides Analyzer mode,Loop-back mode an
 136:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-app/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_can.h ****  * node analysis.
